Files

   README - this file
   LICENSE - copy of the LGPL license
   jmrtd.jar - binary class files
   src/ - sources

Dependencies (might be included in distribution)

   * Requires jdk1.6.

   * Bouncycastle for crypto and ASN1 decoding:
        The jar needs to be in classpath
        Tested with bcprov-jdk16-139.jar.
        URL: http://www.bouncycastle.org/

   * JAI ImageIO for interpreting JPEG 2000 data:
        Needs to be installed in jre/lib,
        jai_imageio.jar in jre/lib/ext, some libs in jre/lib/i386.
        URL: https://jai-imageio.dev.java.net/
        
   * The EJBCA project's CV certificate library:
        Needs to be in classpath.
        Tested with current version of cert-cvc.jar.
        URL: http://ejbca.org/

   * famfamfam.com icons
        GUI code may contain icons by Mark James
        http://www.famfamfam.com/

Optional stuff

   * ApduIO, Java Card simulator
        apduio.jar part of Java Card Kit
        Tested with version 2.2.2
        When making from source, expects a copy or link to this jar
        (or stub) in lib directory.
        http://java.sun.com/javacard/devkit/

   * JCOP toolset
        offcard.jar part of JCOP plugin for Eclipse
        Tested with version 3.1.1
        Tested with version 3.1.2
        When making from source, expects a copy or link to this jar
        (or stub) in lib directory.

   * GlobalPlatform
        gpshell tool for installing to JCOP cards
        http://sourceforge.net/projects/globalplatform/

   * RFIDIOt
        mrpkey.py command line tool for testing/reading/writing/cloning
        http://rfidiot.org/
	
Website

   http://jmrtd.org/
